products.name: Atmosphere Grey
products.intro: Available 16/08 at 11:00 am Streets, courts and everything concrete—we've always loved the ambiance of basketball's roots. Create an aura all your own in the AJ1 'Atmosphere Grey'. The aged aesthetic makes 'em look like you stepped straight out of the jaw-dropping photo of MJ soaring (in Chicago colours, no doubt) above the spray-painted walls and cracked tarmac where dreams begin: the playground. Premium materials, including suede accents, add the finishing touch. The sky's the limit with this one. .
